{"tid":1701941,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【當年今日】柏林圍牆倒下原因：記者會講錯嘢！","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:43:06.000Z","uid":336896,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8306ad7c616dbd881354ae9e2803e140221d5ae6","tid":1701941,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AGBBGoyc9Ps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAGBBGoyc9Ps&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=579f970e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AGBBGoyc9Ps</a><br />\n柏林圍牆倒塌 起因：記者會講錯嘢！<br />\n<br />\n1989年11月9日，本來東德政府只係準備冇簽證限制，俾人民可以自由過關去西柏林。記者問幾時生效，點知個官員口誤，話係即時生效！<br />\n於是，大批群眾湧去關口，關口嘅軍人唔知點辦，唔敢開槍，唯有開放關口俾人通過。因為人潮太多，有人開始拆牆，於是牆就倒了！<br />\n<br />\nPopo 小心啦，終有一日你會喺記者會講錯嘢，成功引爆革命！"},{"pid":"8bcdd06ab92ed7fcf4ef4eb540e5124703cb7021","tid":1701941,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，大家幫忙推"},{"pid":"74f25c095c855f17269b74976f29bfef96c9c279","tid":1701941,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，大家幫忙推"},{"pid":"62e1caee0b10baabf023dee5ac99e8911e11c7d6","tid":1701941,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338e465414bdd1f73fedd37b25e5f5ab23cce75c","tid":1701941,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1698861/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1698861/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n柏林圍牆倒下30週年集會<br />\n德國嘅香港人請多多支持！"},{"pid":"2d806f48b6a0a8dc4d0df6deaf910abbf0ac167c","tid":1701941,"uid":336896,